title: Priebus: Republican Party 'Cooked' If No 2016 White House Win
text:
sharethis 10/17/15 11:00am RNC Chair Reince Priebus says it's all over for his party if they don't win the White House in 2016. In an interview with the Washington Examiner, RNC chair Reince Priebus said it is important to elect Republicans at every level of government, but that the White House is where true power holds court.
